<article class="text">
	<header>
	  <h1>Formulários</h1>
	  <h2>Prefixos e sufixos de campos.</h2>
	</header>
	<p>Você pode extender os campos de formulários adicionando textos antes ou depois do campo.</p>
	<div class="bs-callout bs-callout-danger">
		<h4>Compatibilidade entre navegadores</h4>
		<p>Evite utilizar com o elemento <code>select</code> pois ele não é totalmente customizavel em navegadores Webkit.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="bs-callout bs-callout-info">
		<h4>Tooltips ou Popovers nos grupos de campos precisa de uma configuração especial.</h4>
		<p>Quando você usar tooltips ou popovers nos elementos com a classe <code>.input-group</code>, você terá que especificar a opção <code>container: 'body'</code>para evitar efeitos indesejados.</p>
	</div>
	<h2>Exemplo Básico</h2>
	<br>
	<div class="example">
		<form>
			<div class="input-group">
				<span class="input-group-addon">http://</span>
				<input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="site">
			</div>
			<br>
			<div class="input-group">
				<input type="text" class="form-control">
				<span class="input-group-addon">.00</span>
			</div>
			<br>
			<div class="input-group">
				<span class="input-group-addon">$</span>
				<input type="text" class="form-control">
				<span class="input-group-addon">.00</span>
			</div>
		</form>
	</div>
	<pre class="lang-html prettyprint linenums">
&lt;div class=&quot;input-group&quot;&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;input-group-addon&quot;&gt;http://&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot; placeholder=&quot;site&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;input-group&quot;&gt;
	&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot;&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;input-group-addon&quot;&gt;.00&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;input-group&quot;&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;input-group-addon&quot;&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot;&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;input-group-addon&quot;&gt;.00&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</pre>

	<h2>Modificando o tamanho dos campos</h2>
	<p>Adicionando as classes de tamanho dos campos no elemento com a classe <code>.input-group</code>, seu conteúdo será <s>automagicamente</s> redimencionado.</p>
	<div class="example">
		<form>
			<div class="input-group input-group-lg">
				<span class="input-group-addon">@</span>
				<input type="text" class="form-control input-lg" placeholder="Nome do usuário">
			</div>
			<br>
			<div class="input-group">
				<span class="input-group-addon">@</span>
				<input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Nome do usuário">
			</div>
			<br>
			<div class="input-group input-group-sm">
				<span class="input-group-addon">@</span>
				<input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Nome do usuário">
			</div>
		</form>
	</div>
	<pre class="lang-html prettyprint linenums">
&lt;div class=&quot;input-group input-group-lg&quot;&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;input-group-addon&quot;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;form-control input-lg&quot; placeholder=&quot;Nome do usu&#xe1;rio&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;input-group&quot;&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;input-group-addon&quot;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot; placeholder=&quot;Nome do usu&#xe1;rio&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;input-group input-group-sm&quot;&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;input-group-addon&quot;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot; placeholder=&quot;Nome do usu&#xe1;rio&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</pre>

	<h2>Prefixos com checkbox e radio buttons</h2>
	<p>Basta colocar os checkboxes e radio buttons dentro dos elementos com a classe <code>.input-group-addon</code> para obter o resultado abaixo:</p>
	<div class="example">
		<form>
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-lg-6">
					<div class="input-group">
						<span class="input-group-addon">
							<input type="checkbox">
						</span>
						<input type="text" class="form-control">
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-lg-6">
					<div class="input-group">
						<span class="input-group-addon">
							<input type="radio">
						</span>
						<input type="text" class="form-control">
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</form>
	</div>
	<pre class="lang-html prettyprint linenums">
&lt;div class=&quot;input-group&quot;&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;input-group-addon&quot;&gt;
		&lt;input type=&quot;checkbox&quot;&gt;
	&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;input-group&quot;&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;input-group-addon&quot;&gt;
		&lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot;&gt;
	&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</pre>
	<h2>Prefixos com botões</h2>
	<p>Prefixos e sufixos com botões são um pouco diferentes de serem implementados. Substitua a classe <code>.input-group-addon</code> por <code>.input-group-btn</code> e adicione os botões dentro. Veja como fica:</p>
	<div class="example">
		<form>
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-lg-6">
					<div class="input-group">
						<span class="input-group-btn">
							<button class="btn btn-default" type="button">Valendo!</button>
						</span>
						<input type="text" class="form-control">
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-lg-6">
					<div class="input-group">
						<input type="text" class="form-control">
						<span class="input-group-btn">
							<button class="btn btn-default" type="button">Valendo!</button>
						</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</form>
	</div>
	<pre class="lang-html prettyprint linenums">
&lt;div class=&quot;input-group&quot;&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;input-group-btn&quot;&gt;
		&lt;button class=&quot;btn btn-default&quot; type=&quot;button&quot;&gt;Valendo!&lt;/button&gt;
	&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;input-group&quot;&gt;
	&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot;&gt;
	&lt;span class=&quot;input-group-btn&quot;&gt;
		&lt;button class=&quot;btn btn-default&quot; type=&quot;button&quot;&gt;Valendo!&lt;/button&gt;
	&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</pre>
